een zin in dure schoonheidssalons? <br\/><\/p><p><strong>Met PorePerfect kun je huidonzuiverheden verwijderen, poriën verfijnen en rimpels verminderen. <\/strong>Een grondige reiniging en verzorging zorgt voor een mooie, gladde huid met een gezonde gloed.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19938112438596__8910c77e-b2fc-4472-8267-c8008d6d4123-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":16}},"7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--19900162113860__7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>VOORDELEN<\/strong><\/h3><h5><strong>✔️ Effectieve huidreiniging<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Verkleining van poriën<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Vermindering van rimpels<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Pijnvrij aanbrengen<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Geschikt voor alle huidtypes<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Direct resultaat<\/strong><\/h5><p><\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--19900162113860__7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_1_213409a5-d084-4fae-98fa-5315df8d1855.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"a667d811-a5a8-4eb7-a6c5-1bdd32f113ea":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19938112438596__a667d811-a5a8-4eb7-a6c5-1bdd32f113ea-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>VOORDELEN<\/strong><\/h3><h5><strong>✔️ Effectieve huidreiniging<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Verkleining van poriën<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Vermindering van rimpels<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Pijnvrij aanbrengen<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Geschikt voor alle huidtypes<\/strong><\/h5><h5><strong>✔️ Direct resultaat<\/strong><\/h5><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19938112438596__a667d811-a5a8-4eb7-a6c5-1bdd32f113ea-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":8,"padding_bottom":8}},"16947789000e7c3be1":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"169477810286cbda2b":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"1694778916ae6d13bb":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"2cb68c65-93ce-4030-a625-5bac24b42fe4":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_2_d0f8291b-bc34-4e2f-bee1-448293c0982d.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"center"}},"495da2e8-6942-45a8-96d8-2bf29b5505e6":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"07acd51b-a3b6-4905-bc61-0edd0ef7895b":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>VERHOOG JE WELZIJN<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li><strong>Flawless Skin:  <\/strong>Reinigt de huid, verkleint de poriën, vermindert rimpels en voorkomt huidveroudering. Houdt je huid fris en jong en voorkomt de vorming van puistjes.<\/li><li><strong>Ingebouwde camera: <\/strong> leg je resultaten vast door voor\/na-opnamen te maken of houd je schoonmaakwerkzaamheden in de gaten terwijl je bezig bent. Sluit hem eenvoudig aan op je mobiele telefoon.<\/li><li><strong>6 vacuümsondes: <\/strong> Dankzij de 6 verschillende opzetstukken kan voor elk gezichtsgebied en doel de meest geschikte maat worden geselecteerd.<\/li><li><strong>3 Intensiteitsniveaus: <\/strong> Dankzij de 3 verschillende intensiteiten is de PorePerfect geschikt voor alle huidtypes en huidgevoeligheid. <br\/><\/li><li><strong>Draadloos gebruik: <\/strong>Je kunt hem overal tot 2,5 uur gebruiken. Het apparaat kan worden opgeladen met de meegeleverde USB-kabel.<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["07acd51b-a3b6-4905-bc61-0edd0ef7895b"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"7ead9d52-a3ce-4f63-9e00-e5fbe252c5a8":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_G.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"80d08185-30c8-4c84-a52b-16ca88b3e341":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"dfc5adec-98a8-4ebb-b82a-2915c64e8ecc":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>UW PAKKET BEVAT<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li>1x PorePerfect - huidreiniging en rimpelvermindering<\/li><li>6x verschillende opzetstukken<\/li><li>1x USB-voedingsadapter voor opladen<\/li><li>1x gebruikershandleiding<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["dfc5adec-98a8-4ebb-b82a-2915c64e8ecc"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"9f8ed1f4-75b8-4974-842c-754126d14d2b":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3g_2b9a6877-c3d9-49ea-aaa6-38368ebadb3c.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"791cca60-6f17-4bd8-9106-08a8331c21ee":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19938112438596__791cca60-6f17-4bd8-9106-08a8331c21ee-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>ONZE GARANTIE VOOR U<\/strong><\/h3><p><strong>1.<\/strong>  30 dagen geld-terug-garantie<br\/><strong>2.<\/strong>  Tracking<br\/><strong>3.<\/strong>  Veilige betaalmethoden<br\/><strong>4.<\/strong>  Menselijke klantenservice<br\/><strong>5.<\/strong>  Geen verborgen kosten <\/p><p>Als u vragen heeft, aarzel dan niet om contact met ons op te nemen:  <strong>info@roolo.nl<\/strong><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19938112438596__791cca60-6f17-4bd8-9106-08a8331c21ee-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":0}},"66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>WAT KLANTEN OVER ONZE PORE-PERFECT ZEGGEN:<br\/><\/h3><p>Nog niet overtuigd? Roolo heeft inmiddels ruim  <strong>4200+ tevreden klanten<\/strong>  en dat aantal groeit elke dag! <strong>Dit is wat klanten schrijven over onze Pore-Perfect:<\/strong>  <\/p><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0}},"e21ff573-e051-4bf7-867b-94765a3b8f11":{"type":"icon-bar","blocks":{"template--18472096170313__e21ff573-e051-4bf7-867b-94765a3b8f11-16798645704e6a2246-0":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"chat_bubble","title":"Klantenservice","text":"<p>Uw tevredenheid is onze topprioriteit, mochten er vragen zijn dan kunt u ons gemakkelijk bereiken bij onze contact pagina.<\/p>"}},"template--18472096170313__e21ff573-e051-4bf7-867b-94765a3b8f11-16798645704e6a2246-1":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"truck","title":"Track and Trace","text":"<p>Na aankoop ontvangt u van ons een track and trace code, hiermee kunt u uw order gemakkelijk volgen.<\/p><p><\/p>"}},"template--18472096170313__e21ff573-e051-4bf7-867b-94765a3b8f11-16798645704e6a2246-2":{"type":"column","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon":"heart","title":"Icon","text":"<p>Pair text with an icon to focus 